Privacy Policy
Effective Date: 7 January 2025

This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use Pomilo-Boost Your Focus Watch App ("the App").

1. No Personal Data Collection
We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This app does not collect, store, or share any personal data. We do not gather any personally identifiable information such as your name, email address, or any other sensitive data.

2. App Functionality
The App is designed to help you improve focus and manage your time by providing a timer-based productivity tool. It does not require any registration or login to use, and all features are available immediately after installation. There are no third-party integrations or services that require data collection or access to your device information.

3. No Third-Party Service Providers
We do not share any data with third-party service providers, advertisers, or analytics services. The App operates independently without reliance on third-party data analytics or advertising platforms.

4. Data Security
As we do not collect any personal or sensitive information, there is no data stored that could be compromised. The App works offline and does not transmit any user data over the internet.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
If we decide to change this Privacy Policy, we will post an updated version on this page. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting. We encourage users to periodically check this page for updates.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or need further clarification, please contact us at:

